column2: SELECT TOP #   e.SystemStudentID as StudentID,   e.GradeLevel as EnrollmentGrade,   e.SchoolYear4Digit as SchoolYear4Digit,   t.TestPeriod as Period,   t.TestSubjectGroup as AssessmentSubject,   TableName as MetricSource,   t.TestType as MetricName,   e.SystemStudentID as Score,   e.SystemStudentID as IsMostRecent FROM Enrollment as e JOIN TestScores as t ON e.SystemStudentID = t.SystemStudentID
